05:48.095 --> 06:14.727
Chancellor felt like that they, being the 
University of Texas System, would like to take the

05:48.095 --> 06:14.727
lead in international trade and therefore would 
like to have Laredo State University in their

05:48.095 --> 06:14.727
system.

