06:24.155 --> 06:35.231
University had almost become a part of the 
University of Texas system some years earlier and

06:24.155 --> 06:35.231
there had always been that close tie. Number two, 
the state senator in the Lareda area was a graduate

06:36.333 --> 06:45.186
of the University of Texas system and would 
probably lean toward putting Laredo in the

06:45.436 --> 06:52.686
University of Texas system. The A&I University 
